* Torii cedars of Hatsuma Kinomiya Shrine (city-designated natural monument<ref name="tennen"/>)

=== Festivals ===
* Annual grand festival (around October 19)

=== Access ===
* {{ill|lt=Tōkai Bus|Q11527778|qid=Q11527778|1=Tokai Bus}} (city-commissioned self-operated route<ref>[https://www.at-s.com/news/article/shizuoka/932289.html Route bus Nakaizu Line to be city-operated] - Shizuoka Shimbun 2021/7/21</ref>): 3-5 minutes on foot northeast from “Nakazato” or “Hatsuma” bus stops.

